snippet.title: Amber Heard Gets Destroyed By Johnny Depp Fans At Fashion Show
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Gets Destroyed By Johnny Depp Fans At Fashion Show

Amber Heard's chances of convincing people that she was the victim of violence in her relationship with Johnny Depp have all but vanished. Now the tables have turned, as Amber Heard has recently failed miserably! Amber Heard was invited to model for L'Oreal Paris at Paris Fashion Week's Le Defile L'Oreal Paris Womenswear Spring/Summer 2022. However, Johnny Depp's followers were not pleased to see her and booed her! As the designer showcases hit the streets of Paris, the annual Paris Fashion Week was back and better than ever.
The event lasted from September 28 through October 6. As usual, the historic fashion event attracted a slew of celebrities dressed to the nines in their finest ensembles. The event had a spot for everyone at its table, from Oscar-winning actress Helen Mirren to the most current Cinderella, Camilla Cabello, but of course there was the face from many years ago, Amber Heard! But there was some drama, and we'll tell you all about it right now!
